author: Squidmar Miniatures
description:
Follow the Paradise campaign on gamefound before it starts, and back it to get a free copy of the exclusive miniature of Kyra Rhust. The campaign starts on June 18th: https://gamefound.com/en/projects/mindwork-games/paradise---a-wastepunk-boardgame

We asked some of our favorite Warhammer painters on Fiverr to paint our epic dragon. To make warhammer conversions or just paint the miniature as cool as possible. And here's what we got. 

Javi Paints: https://go.fiverr.com/visit/?bta=64219&brand=fp&landingPage=https%253A%252F%252Fwww.fiverr.com%252Fjavipaintsminis
